UID:1Im_IpY3NQjcR2bxXjgY8
SUMMARY:Artist Alley Houston III
DTSTAMP:20260701T101451Z
DTSTART:20260711T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Artist Alley Houston III — 100+ Local Creators. All Original. A
	ll Handmade.\nPrint hunters\, charm collectors\, plushie lovers\, and fand
	om art fanatics — Artist Alley Houston III is your weekend. Two days\, 100
	+ local and regional creators\, and zero mass-produced merch. Every piece 
	on every table was made by the person standing behind it. \n  \n📅 Date: Sa
	turday–Sunday\, July 11–12\, 2026 \n⏰ Time: Saturday: 10AM – 6PM | Sunday:
	 10AM – 5PM \n📍 Location: 9700 Bissonnet St\, Unit 1500\, Houston\, TX 770
	36 🎟️ FREE Entry + FREE Parking \n  \n🔥 Event Highlights 🔥 \n🎨 100+ Artists
	 and Makers — All Fandoms\, All Styles Explore a curated marketplace packe
	d with anime fan art\, original illustrations\, stickers\, enamel pins\, a
	rt prints\, zines\, plushies\, handcrafted charms\, crochet creations\, ac
	cessories\, fantasy artwork\, and pop-culture-inspired pieces — all origin
	al\, all handmade\, no AI-generated art. Whether you’re shopping for your 
	wall\, your ita bag\, your shelf\, or just yourself\, this floor delivers.
	 Come ready to discover your next favorite Houston creator. \n  \n✨ Exclus
	ive Drops and Event Debuts Many artists are launching event-only merch\, l
	imited bundles\, brand-new releases\, and first-time debuts created specif
	ically for Artist Alley Houston III. You won’t find these anywhere else — 
	online or in stores. Bring a tote bag. You’re going to need it. \n  \n💬 Me
	et the Makers Talk with the artists. Hear the stories behind the work. Com
	mission something made just for you. This is not just a shopping floor — i
	t’s where Houston’s creative community shows up in person. Fellow creators
	\, longtime collectors\, and first-time visitors all belong here. \n  \n🎁 
	FREE Artist Raffle Win original art\, stickers\, keychains\, and handmade 
	goods donated by our featured artists. No purchase necessary — just stop b
	y\, sign up\, and you’re in. Every ticket is a chance to go home with some
	thing one-of-a-kind. \n  \n💌 Join the Artist Lineup Table space is open fo
	r local artists and makers. Come build with the Houston creative community
	. 👉 Apply here \n  \n🏨 Traveling to Houston? Lock In Your Rate We’ve secur
	ed a special hotel rate exclusively for Artist Alley Houston III attendees
	. Book your stay and make it a full weekend. 👉 Book here \n  \nTwo days. 1
	00+ creators. Art made with love\, sold in person. Artist Alley Houston II
	I — July 11 & 12.\n\nhttps://ccs-houston.com/events/artist-alley-houston-i
	ii/\n\nFrom CCS Houston
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/artist-alley-houston-iii/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:ccs-houston
CATEGORIES:CCS Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT31H
END:VEVENT
