BEGIN:VEVENT
IMAGE;VALUE=URI;DISPLAY=BADGE;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ccs-houston.com/wp
 -content/uploads/2026/04/HTX-Event-Launch-Kit-CCS-TCG-Con-X-1.jpg
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ccs-houston.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/0
 4/HTX-Event-Launch-Kit-CCS-TCG-Con-X-1.jpg
UID:qLTdyxzbpXx03z6PreEQj
SUMMARY:Houston TCG Con X
DTSTAMP:20260701T101452Z
DTSTART:20260807T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:🃏 Houston TCG Con X | Every Format. One Floor. Three Days. 🃏\nT
	hree days. Every format in the room. The Houston TCG community takes over 
	CCS August 7–9 for Pokémon\, MTG\, One Piece\, Lorcana\, and Yu-Gi-Oh. Tou
	rnament grinders and binder flippers on the same floor\, doing what this c
	ommunity does best. \n  \n📅 Date: Friday–Sunday\, August 7–9\, 2026 \n⏰ Ti
	me: Friday: 3PM–10PM | Saturday: 10AM–6PM | Sunday: 10AM–5PM \n📍 Location:
	 9700 Bissonnet St\, Unit 1500\, Houston\, TX \n🎟️ FREE Entry + FREE Parkin
	g \n  \n🔥 Event Highlights 🔥 \n🃔 Multi-Game Vendor Floor \nPokémon. MTG. O
	ne Piece. Lorcana. Yu-Gi-Oh. Singles vendors\, sealed product\, and binder
	 traders across every major format. Three full days to hunt\, flip\, and d
	eal face-to-face. \n  \n🏆 Multi-Game Tournaments \nCompetitive rounds runn
	ing all weekend across formats. Tournament schedule and registration detai
	ls coming soon. Follow CCS Houston for updates. \n  \n📦 Full Marketplace \
	nSports cards\, anime merch\, figures\, comics\, and toys rounding out the
	 vendor floor for everything you collect beyond the card game. \n  \n💼 Ven
	dor Tables Available \nTCG dealers\, singles vendors\, sports card sellers
	\, anime and collectible booths. Houston’s biggest TCG weekend is yours. A
	pply: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdei0apYj2qU4fQIiz9rrqVDHgq
	mFZSpLRzYDAufcg3B8BaXA/viewform \n  \n🏨 Traveling to Houston? Lock Your Ro
	om \nGroup rate available at Marriott. Book before it fills: https://www.m
	arriott.com/event-reservations/reservation-link.mi?id=1767823967549&key=CO
	RP&app=resvlink \nThree days\, every format\, free entry. See you in Augus
	t\, Houston.\n\nhttps://ccs-houston.com/events/houston-tcg-con-x/\n\nFrom 
	CCS Houston
